                    </svg>
                    <h2>Provide you with new carrier opportunities</h2>
                    <p>
                        If opportunity doesn't knock, build a door.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <svg class="bd-placeholder-img" width="140" height="140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder: 140x140" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <title>signpost</title>
                        <path d="M7 16h2V6h5a1 1 0 0 0 .8-.4l.975-1.3a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.6L14.8 2.4A1 1 0 0 0 14 2H9v-.586a1 1 0 0 0-2 0V7H2a1 1 0 0 0-.8.4L.225 8.7a.5.5 0 0 0 0 .6l.975 1.3a1 1 0 0 0 .8.4h5v5z" />
                    </svg>

                    <h2>Find work that suits you.</h2>
                    <p>
                        Do what you love, and you’ll never work another day in your life.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr class="featurette-divider">

            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Apply for a job. <span class="text-muted">All your needs in one place.</span></h2>
                    <p class="lead">
                        We work with companies to bring you only the best offers with no red tape.
                        You can apply for jobs and internships directly from our website.
                        Upload your CV and motivational letter all in one place.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <svg class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" width="400" height="400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <title>Building</title>
